{#- Expects: w (WatchlistEntry), price (PriceSnapshot|None), tags (tuple[str]),
              pattern_tag (str|None — Phase 4 Task 4.7; spec §3.5 SIBLING to tags).

   Phase 13 T2.SB6c T-A.6c.2 Gap A.3 — also reads `vm.watchlist_chart_svg_bytes`
   (Mapping[ticker, bytes]) when present in the enclosing scope (DashboardVM
   or WatchlistVM both populate it from chart_renders cache). The row gains a
   compact thumbnail column when bytes are available; omitted otherwise so
   pre-cache callers still render unchanged.

   Phase 13 T-T4.SB.3 (Item 5 + Item 6) — also accepts a direct
   `chart_svg_bytes_for_row` context var from the /watchlist/{ticker}/row
   collapse route (which has no enclosing `vm` — the route renders a single
   row via build_watchlist_row + JIT cache lookup); without this the
   collapse path's thumbnail would render blank after expand. -#}
{% set _thumb_bytes = chart_svg_bytes_for_row if chart_svg_bytes_for_row is defined and chart_svg_bytes_for_row else (vm.watchlist_chart_svg_bytes.get(w.ticker) if vm is defined and vm.watchlist_chart_svg_bytes else None) %}
<tr id="watchlist-row-{{ w.ticker }}"
    hx-get="/watchlist/{{ w.ticker }}/expand" hx-swap="outerHTML"
    hx-headers='{"HX-Request": "true"}'>
  <td>
    {# Phase 13 T-T4.SB.5 Item 4: lightning glyph removed per operator
       OQ-X.1 LOCK. Thumbnail cell preserved. #}
    {% if _thumb_bytes %}
      <span class="watchlist-thumbnail">{{ _thumb_bytes.decode('utf-8') | safe }}</span>
    {% endif %}
  </td>
  <td>{{ w.ticker }}</td>
  <td>
    {% if price %}
      ${{ '%.2f' | format(price.price) }}
      {% if price.is_stale %}<span class="stale">(stale)</span>{% endif %}
    {% else %}—{% endif %}
  </td>
  <td>{% if current_pivot is not none %}${{ '%.2f' | format(current_pivot) }}{% elif w.entry_target %}${{ '%.2f' | format(w.entry_target) }}{% else %}—{% endif %}</td>
  <td>
    {% if price and w.entry_target %}
      {{ '%.1f' | format(((price.price - w.entry_target) / w.entry_target) * 100) }}%
    {% else %}—{% endif %}
  </td>
  <td>{{ '%.2f' | format(w.last_adr_pct or 0) }}</td>
  <td>
    {{ tags | join(' · ') }}
    {%- if pattern_tag is defined and pattern_tag %}
      {%- if tags %} · {% endif -%}
      <span class="tag tag-pattern">{{ pattern_tag }}</span>
    {%- endif %}
  </td>
  <td>
    <button onclick="event.stopPropagation()"
            hx-get="/trades/entry/form?ticker={{ w.ticker }}"
            hx-target="closest tr" hx-swap="outerHTML"
            hx-headers='{"HX-Request": "true"}'>Enter</button>
  </td>
</tr>
